Hong Kong Rejects Plan for Electricity Rate Hike, RTHK Says

-- B y   S h a i   O s t e r
-- 
2011-12-13T11:42:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/hong-kong-rejects-plan-for-electricity-rate-hike-rthk-says.html
Hong Kong ’s government has rejected
calls for higher electricity tariffs from power providers CLP
Holdings Ltd. and Hong Kong Electric Co., a unit of Power Assets
Holdings Ltd., Radio Television Hong Kong reported without
naming its source.  The government found proposals for price increases by the
two were “unacceptable,” RTHK quoted the source as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shai Oster in Hong Kong at 
 soster@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
